{"tid":114753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真豬勁過港豬]  為被殺同伴報仇　大豬幼豬圍攻分食大蟒蛇","createTime":"2017-02-10T04:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T05:42:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c43ec73561daa54605c517f2d4078f68038abf14","tid":114753,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170210/bknint-20170210030338323-0210_17011_001.html?eventsection=int_news&amp;eventid=402883474cd641ed014cdef8e2934d7a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170210%2Fbknint-20170210030338323-0210_17011_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dint_news%26eventid%3D402883474cd641ed014cdef8e2934d7a&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=de6205c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170210/bknint-20170210030338323-0210_17011_001.html?eventsection=int_news&amp;eventid=402883474cd641ed014cdef8e2934d7a</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170210/photo/bknint-20170210030338323-0210_17011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170210%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170210030338323-0210_17011_001_01p.jpg&h=ad516b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對同類慘遭殺害，原來看似懶洋洋的豬隻都會團結一致，為自己人報仇。網上近日流傳片段，指有最少8隻豬為剛被殺害的小豬報仇，圍攻殺豬兇手大蟒蛇，並且將其分屍。<br />\n<br />\n片中可見，一群最少8隻的豬不停圍攻一條蟒蛇，用有力的下巴狂咬蛇身，並把蟒蛇撕開。從蟒蛇裂開的腹部見到，仍有相信是一隻小豬的屍體。據悉，豬群是因為其中一隻小豬被蟒蛇食掉，才憤而攻擊報復。<br />\n<br />\n有網民看過片段後，直指片段驚人。暫未知片段拍攝地點，估計是在去年攝於泰國東部或老撾。"},{"pid":"48f0a2bca6d9ae8ba6563f8553e2feb1151aa987","tid":114753,"uid":41420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:46:19.000Z","msg":"唔好再叫香港人做港豬，侮辱左豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7bae9994b8abe6f63c9d022e6ca64c2691f933","tid":114753,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:48:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":